changelog.change_log:
- Oculus reports have been resolved;
- the inputs of the controllers and hands have been aligned and reinserted the grips of the objects so that they are natural;
- the buttons on the table have been inserted to switch to the restaurant and kitchen maps;
- some situations have been resolved in which the gripping hand and the hand controlled by the user both remained visible;
- the demo end screen has been modified to not require an input but only a 10 second wait, after which you are returned to the training room.
